}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Center\", \"from\": 4415, \"to\": 4430}, {\"ngram\": \"SafeSport Code.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Van de Velde\", \"from\": 4435, \"to\": 4466}, {\"ngram\": \"a husband\", \"from\": 4478, \"to\": 4487}, {\"ngram\": \"father\", \"from\": 4492, \"to\": 4498}, {\"ngram\": \"his victim\", \"from\": 4500, \"to\": 4510}]}, {\"sentence\": \"At the time of sentencing, the court heard testimony that she had been self-harming since the incident.\", \"from\": 4519, \"to\": 4622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 4522, \"to\": 4530}, {\"ngram\": \"sentencing\", \"from\": 4534, \"to\": 4544}, {\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 4546, \"to\": 4555}, {\"ngram\": \"testimony\", \"from\": 4562, \"to\": 4571}, {\"ngram\": \"the incident\", \"from\": 4609, \"to\": 4621}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The judgetoldvan de Velde: \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe emotional harm that has been caused to this child is enormous.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d In a 2018interviewwith Dutch broadcaster NOS, van de Velde called the rape \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthe biggest mistake of my young life,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d and said \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t reverse it, so I have to live with the consequences.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 I can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t get around it.\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4747, \"end\": 4752, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"score\": 0.9940577675347285, \"rank\": 0.005277742352251819, \"text\": \"Dutch\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dutch_language\"}, {\"begin\": 4765, \"end\": 4768, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8961066656899908e-15, \"text\": \"NOS\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\", \"Q141683\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nederlandse_Omroep_Stichting\"}, {\"begin\": 4770, \"end\": 4782, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"score\": 0.9999795909488899, \"rank\": 2.0409467432898144e-05, \"text\": \"van de Velde\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charles_William_Meredith_van_de_Velde\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The judgetoldvan de Velde\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4648}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cThe emotional harm\", \"from\": 4650, \"to\": 4671}, {\"ngram\": \"this child\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4706}, {\"ngram\": \"enormous.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 4710, \"to\": 4722}, {\"ngram\": \"the rape\", \"from\": 4789, \"to\": 4797}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthe biggest mistake\", \"from\": 4798, \"to\": 4820}, {\"ngram\": \"my young life\", \"from\": 4824, \"to\": 4837}, {\"ngram\": \"can\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t\", \"from\": 4856, \"to\": 4863}, {\"ngram\": \"the consequences.\\u00e2\\u0080\", \"from\": 4899, \"to\": 4918}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I can also keep blaming myself a hundred thousand times for it happening and how it happened.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d He said he thought the girl was older when he first met her online, and when she said she was 12, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cI was really shocked, so I immediately broke off contact.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d But then he resumed communication, and he decided to go to England.\", \"from\": 4946, \"to\": 5273, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5265, \"end\": 5272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_England\", \"score\": 0.9856413321354742, \"rank\": 0.0141783463409592, \"text\": \"England\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_England\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kingdom_of_England\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a hu